story_parts.text: I was never one for staying in one place for too long. As soon as I turned 18, I packed my bags and set off on an adventure. I had no idea where I was going or what I was looking for, but I knew I would find it. I hitchhiked my way across the country, hopping from one ride to the next. I slept in fields and on couches, never staying in one place for more than a few days. I met some interesting people
